      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>Player</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>You can call me a player </l>
          <l>Or you can call me whenever you want to make a new start </l>
          <l>Vampire slayer but I've got no intention of driving a stake </l>
          <l>through your heart </l>
          <l>Can't be your teacher 'cuz I'm my own damned student and </l>
          <l>I've got a lot left to learn </l>
          <l>I won't be a preacher - my religious bridges have all been </l>
          <l>burned </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>Am I freakin' you out girl? Are things movin' too fast? </l>
          <l>I can't relieve the doubt you feel, it's somethin' from </l>
          <l>your past </l>
          <l>Something that won't last </l>
          <l>Something that must pass </l>
          <l>This too shall pass </l>
        </lg>
        <lg Chorus="yes" number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>I love you girl...</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
    </body>
